Name: Administer Products

Short Description: The owner wishes to administer products.

Precondition: none

Postcondition: A product has been administered.

Error Condition: A product has not been administered.

System state on error condition: Product is not changed or created.

Actors: Owner

Trigger: Owner wishes to administer a product.

Standard procedure:
(1) Owner searches for product.
(2) Product is found.
(3) Owner administers the product.
(4) Owner safes the changes.

Alternate procedure:
(2') Product is not found. 
(3') Owner creates the product. 